thread.title: BRIEF-Deluxe Family sees FY 2017 net profit up 50 pct to 80 pct

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Deluxe Family sees FY 2017 net profit up 50 pct to 80 pct
text:
Jan 30 (Reuters) - Deluxe Family Co Ltd
* Says it sees net profit for FY 2017 to increase by 50 percent to 80 percent, or to be 192.8 million yuan to 231.8 million yuan
* Says the net profit of FY 2016 was 128.8 million yuan
* Comments that increased real estate income and dividend of Xiamen-based bank firm as main reasons for the forecast
